{
  "chapter": 57,
  "chapter_summary": "第五十七回 归途中。芮玮功力大进，击败欧阳龙年。众人乘船回归中原，途中欧阳龙年设宴试探芮玮是否得到玄龟集，并试图离间芮玮与玉面神婆的关系。叶青怀孕，被欧阳龙年发现并以此要挟芮玮交出玄龟集。铁网帮船队出现，带来新的变数。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "爹爹，爹爹……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "月余不见，你们好吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是不是青姐？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然是啦，难道以为我是鬼吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说来话长，咱们先去看看大哥怎么了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他骤然得胜，怕是欢喜得傻了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "爹爹死了，爹爹死了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那怎么办？那怎么办？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你把他抱上船，等咱们上了你的船，再替你父亲救活。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥别放他走，他要是将船开走，咱们就糟了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不会，他还需要我去救他父亲。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "月余不见大哥，大哥在哪里过的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们发现无名老人住在里面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想是因为吃了一种白色怪鱼的原故。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么怪鱼呀？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吃不得……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么吃不得？大哥能吃，我怎么不能吃？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能吃……就是不能吃……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对，快去看看蒋老前辈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老前辈好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那厚脸皮的老儿被芮大哥打死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的吗？你用什么功力将他打死？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有打死，只是受了内伤，闭住了气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈据实而言，岂敢欺蒙前辈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老夫第一杯酒向救命恩人敬。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "坐下，坐下，不用客气。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "芮老弟，还是敬你一杯。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一桌酒不吃完，谁敢告辞。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥，咱们走吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们两个坐下，听这老儿要说什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对，不吃也该听主人说完话再走。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刘忠柱、蒋老婆子和老夫只能斗个平手……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你敢说能胜过芮兄吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要说什么赶快说，啰嗦什么！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "转向玉面神婆道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么啦？怎么啦……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我问你，芮玮当真没有见着玄龟集？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥人最老实，前辈还不信他的话？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道为什么想吐？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道，敢情病了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这不是病，你有身孕。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "几个月了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要是真的，快二个月了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叶青呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没见到！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事，丢了东西吗？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在我床上？我床上从不睡不要脸的女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说谁不要脸！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怀了身孕？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，确实怀了身孕。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "玄龟集在哪里，她就在哪里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一句老话，交出玄龟集，就让你们见面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没见过玄龟集，你还不相信吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鬼才相信你没见过玄龟集。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要怎样才相信芮某的话？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除非剜出心肝表明，咱们才信！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么说来，芮某拿不出玄龟集，非死不成？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么船？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来船旗语说，是铁网帮的船。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁网帮一向在长江活动，这次来到大海做什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_fu",
      "speaker_name": "船夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说是帮主的女儿出海游玩，叫咱们回避。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叫咱们回避！知不知道咱们是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_fu",
      "speaker_name": "船夫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卑下已告诉他们，说是当年海龙王的船。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    }
  ],
